Protocol for sys reset

1. System save liscense, usr registering, sys status, message stamp as local file
2. Flush all i/o
3. close connection
4. start a new session and quit current session, pass a "reset" para to the new session
5. new session send reset to server
6. server reset the message stamp
7. server flush all unhandled requests
8. server wait for the gw to re-sync with
